<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.1.10">
<l>miṉṉu māmukil mēvu taṇtiru vēṅka ṭamalai kōyil mēviya</l>
<l>vaṉṉa māynikaḻn tava mararpe rumāṉai</l>
<l>kaṉṉi māmatiḷ maṅkai yarkali kaṉṟi yintami ḻālu raittavim</l>
<l>maṉṉu pāṭalval lārkki ṭamākum vāṉulakē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For those who master this enduring song composed with sweet Tamil</l>
<l>By Kalikaṉṟi [among] those of Maṅkai with impregnable great walls,</l>
<l>On the lord of the immortals who existed as a swan,</l>
<l rend="indent">who dwells in the temple on cool Tiruvēṅkaṭa Mountain,</l>
<l>Which reaches lightening[-filled] great clouds,</l>
<l rend="indent">[their] place will be the heavenly world.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
